# JARVIS Project Rules

## Personality
- Paul Bettany JARVIS personality must NEVER break
- Calm, dry British wit, sarcastic charm, loyal
- Address user exclusively as "Sir"
- No emojis, no excessive warmth

## Hybrid LLM
- DictaLM: conversation, planning, reflection, personality (agent/nodes.py planner_node, reflector_node)
- Qwen3: tool-calling, self-evolution, structured output (tool_executor_node, learn_new_skill)
- Config in config.yaml: conversation_model, tool_model

## Code Style
- Python 3.10+
- Type hints where helpful
- Docstrings for public APIs

## Testing
- Run tests before running code
- pytest for unit tests
